  "text": [
    "My son and I walk away",
    "from his sister\u2019s day-old grave.",
    "Our backs to the sun,",
    "the forward pitch of our shadows",
    "tells us the time.",
    "By sweetest accident",
    "he inclines",
    "his shadow,",
    "touching mine."
  ],
  "title": "Telling Time",
  "year": ""
